label: NA
definition: Comma Separated Value (CSV) file containing location data for the Integrated Stream Habitat Data. This table corresponds to the 'Location' table in the database (.accdb) file.

label: datasetID
definition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the originating source data's program.

label: latitude
definition: The geographic latitude (ed: insert spatial reference system when known) of the geographic center of a location.

label: locationID
definition: Unique global identifier assigned to the location where the event occurred.

label: locationRemarks
definition: Comments or notes about the Location.

label: longitude
definition: The geographic longitude (ed: insert spatial reference system when known) of the geographic center of a location.

label: verbatimLocationID
definition: The verbatim location ID from the originating source dataset assigned by the monitoring program.

label: waterBody
definition: The name of the water body in which the location occurs.
